=80=99re headed. In Loose Bannon ( https://puck.news/steve-bannon-on-his-pl=
ans-to-humanely-deport-10-million-people/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Backstory+-+SU=
BSCRIBERS+%2811%2F30%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281=
1%2F16%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=
=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ), Peter=E2=80=99s chat with the MAGA Rasputin render=
s the most complete explanation for how Trump will deploy tariffs and weapo=
nize Elon and Vivek against Washington; how he=E2=80=99ll play chicken with=
 his party in the Senate, and exercise his deportation revolver.

Meanwhile, in Elon Irritations
& Epshteyn=E2=80=99s Overreach ( https://puck.news/elon-musk-irritations-bo=
ris-epshteyns-overreach/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2=
F30%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F16%2F24%29&ut=
m_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd=
12a ), Tara Palmeri offers a vivid look inside Mar-a-Lago=E2=80=99s shock-a=
nd-awe decision-making structure=E2=80=94an unsurprisingly amorphous confed=
eration where Susie Wiles is feeling out her influence and many are openly =
wondering when the president-elect will lose patience with =E2=80=9CUncle E=
lon,=E2=80=9D who is now a fixture on the patio. Bill Cohan=E2=80=99s brill=
iant piece, The Apollo Moon Landing That Wasn=E2=80=99t ( https://puck.news=
/inside-the-meeting-between-trump-and-apollos-marc-rowan/?utm_campaign=3DTh=
e+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F30%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Backstory+-+=
SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F16%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcusto=
mer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ), offers subscribers a privileged vie=
w
inside the room where Marc Rowan lost the Treasury sweepstakes in Palm Beac=
h.

As before, Trump is threatening to remake our economy and politics, and eve=
rything in between, in his own
image, according to his own whims. This is why, as Eriq Gardner recently no=
ted, the media industry is beginning to take note of the news emanating fro=
m the Leonard L. Williams Justice Center in Wilmington. A year ago, Fox New=
s prepared to defend itself against Dominion Voting Systems in the same cou=
rthouse. (As you=E2=80=99ll recall, the company settled for $787 million be=
fore defenestrating its chief legal and policy officer.) This time around, =
Rupert Murdoch and his lieutenants are accused of breaching fiduciary dutie=
s by pandering to Trump with a steady diet of misinformation. Company share=
holders suggest that the board ignored all sorts of defamation risks, which=
 led to the Dominion settlement, among other exorbitant legal headaches.

And yet, as Eriq notes in A New Murdoch Suit & R.F.K.=E2=80=99s Cable Bomb =
( https://puck.news/a-new-fox-news-legal-headache-over-2020-disinformation/=
?utm_campaign=3DThe+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F30%2F24%29&utm_content=
=3DThe+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F16%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action=
&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ), amid the changin=
g legal tides anticipated during Trump II=E2=80=94an antagonistic F.C.C. an=
d the derivative implications of House resolution 9495, to name but a coupl=
e=E2=80=94many in the media industry may actually be pulling for the Murdoc=
hs.

But if you only have time to read one piece this weekend, and you=E2=80=99r=
e politically sated for the moment, I=E2=80=99d turn your attention to Laur=
en Sherman=E2=80=99s latest masterpiece, Blazy Saddles ( https://puck.news/=
matthieu-blazy-to-chanel-signs-point-to-yes/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Backstory+-=
+SUBSCRIBERS+%2811%2F30%2F24%29&utm_content=3DThe+Backstory+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%=
2811%2F16%2F24%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_te=
rm=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ), about the emergence of Matthieu Blazy as the lea=
ding contender for the vacant Chanel
creative director role. In its own right, the Chanel search is an outlier a=
mid the larger transformation among creative industries to professionalize,=
 eliminate the key man risk of a singular design voice, and manage costs an=
d supply chain economics as critically as what=E2=80=99s on the rack. This =
is one of the great stories of our time, and precisely what you should expe=
ct to read in Puck.

Have a great weekend,
Jon

